    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>Dark Mass</strong>》是一款第一人称心理恐怖游戏，将你带入深海之中令人不安的寂静，这里时间静止，遗忘的恐惧等待着你。你将扮演潜水探险家艾丽丝，她与哥哥里德在地震后发现了一艘沉船的遗迹。然而废墟之下隐藏着更加恐怖的东西：一座沉没的庄园，历经数世纪依旧完好无损。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879940/extras/0441180caa7cb39978c0807162dc8cbb.poster.avif?t=1771520624\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879940/extras/0441180caa7cb39978c0807162dc8cbb.webm?t=1771520624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879940/extras/0441180caa7cb39978c0807162dc8cbb.mp4?t=1771520624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入庄园后，艾丽丝很快意识到自己并不孤单。无情的存在潜伏在黑暗中，被诅咒困在此地。要逃离这里，她必须挖掘过去，解开以真实历史酷刑为灵感的仪式谜题，并做出道德抉择，这将决定她的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879940/extras/7159b0e81ba4315dcd063c31b7d6eac3.poster.avif?t=1771520624\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879940/extras/7159b0e81ba4315dcd063c31b7d6eac3.webm?t=1771520624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879940/extras/7159b0e81ba4315dcd063c31b7d6eac3.mp4?t=1771520624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深海恐惧症</strong>：首款完全水下的恐怖游戏，垂直探索带来新层次的紧张体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>带选择的叙事探索</strong>：通过完全西班牙语配音的无线电与哥哥交流，揭开深海秘密。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>令人不安的仪式谜题</strong>：破解受宗教审判酷刑启发的独特挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恐怖的存在</strong>：躲避或击败被困数世纪的悲惨怪物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>决定命运的选择</strong>：你的行动影响结局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>虚幻引擎5</strong>：前所未有的海洋环境和海洋生物的真实感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879940/extras/8512c590d23d93b930d72488ff42e12a.poster.avif?t=1771520624\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879940/extras/8512c590d23d93b930d72488ff42e12a.webm?t=1771520624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879940/extras/8512c590d23d93b930d72488ff42e12a.mp4?t=1771520624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能否逃出深渊，还是会成为被遗忘的灵魂？</p>",
